Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Turn 24\NDamocles之空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗  扇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我有指挥大家避难的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是我对不起你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们卷入了F.L.E.I.J.A.所支配的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…F.L.E.I.J.A.吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托瓦米舰队被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战将如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战将继续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Avalon保持后退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持与Damocles之间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部队展开轮番攻势  迫使Damocles持续发射F.L.E.I.J.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么…轻易地就…由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉  接下来的发射准备完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战术起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只要突入敌军腹地就用不了F.L.E.I.J.A.了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLAZELUMINOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（樱导能源盾：利用樱导矿产生的能量场形成的能源盾）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此巨大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damocles原本就是为了掌控绝对的制空权而制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它继续提升高度的话  我们会束手无策的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  能突破那障壁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在试了  但是与对方的功率比值相差太过悬殊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这种状态下应该无法再发射F.L.E.I.J.A.了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的攻击也无效  跟旁观没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界只能在F.L.E.I.J.A.压倒性的恐怖中沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也算是一种和平的状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让残存兵力以Avalon为中心集结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同人质一起对Damocles发动突击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你回来了  说明已经有头绪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最后还要看陛下和朱雀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈泽尔  你打算连人质一起消灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今黑之骑士团已经被击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没输
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就多等10分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有10分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经取得反击位置才来联系我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  10分钟是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把下一轮发射所需的10分钟卖了个高价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是做好战后处理的准备而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思是说黑之骑士团已经不需要了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为集合体的军事力量有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  迪巴鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  会长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学生会成员正以世界为敌战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是挖苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没能保护妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不都很努力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是努力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你已经努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要亲自
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包抄过来了吗  星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不让你击沉Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻  由我来阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这无道之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种状态  亏你还能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经丑陋到舍弃祖国  单纯的执着于地位了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望何在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下只是在寻求未来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所寻求的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  该赞一下他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一浮空装置受损
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损伤率75%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会坠落吗  这Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着慢着慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  给我们的因缘做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有志气的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们进到里面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入白刃战就有胜机了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压制动力和通信系统  去救人质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑到这里就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰就此降落到太平洋上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去执行Apate Aletheia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（Apate： 希腊神话中欺瞒之女神；  Aletheia：真实之女神）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路以来  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里能发射吗  F.L.E.I.J.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经张开了BLAZELUMINOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到临界点为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  虽然是让黑之骑士团消失的良机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能太贪心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我个人的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是尤菲米亚殿下的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我必须去做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那个的最终程序必须输入环境数据才能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你刚才的话中我已经理解了你的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你能帮助  我这个尤菲的仇敌Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法原谅Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许一辈子都无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  恨归恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我必须要找到自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇  你在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是重要的战斗力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  所以我来取那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦你护卫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许要亲手杀死娜娜莉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她要做零之镇魂曲的障碍也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修  你不恨我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赐予了你Geass  大大地改变了你的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你啊  明明是个魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.  因为有你给我的Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有你  我才能迈出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事  一切都由我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次遇到像你这样的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华莲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我  到Damocles去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  以红莲为对手…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能担心我  我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一定要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说要给我笑容的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一招  无论如何都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌Knight Mare编队正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先锋是蜃气楼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:09:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把F.L.E.I.J.A.发射口的BLAZELUMINOUS  部分解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标改为蜃气楼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修  最后要舍身一击了吗  丑态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标变更  完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉  这样就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  修奈泽尔皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLAZELUMINOUS  解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  输入数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F.L.E.I.J.A.每时每刻都在改变着结构
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要破坏其对应的结构反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能停止F.L.E.I.J.A.的临界反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  必须在离爆炸约19秒时把现场环境数据输入程序
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而就算程序完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实行时间也只有0.04秒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平…完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原理上应该是可行的  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米亚殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F.L.E.I.J.A.…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了  成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19秒和0.04秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还准备了这种玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在  冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破BLAZE了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,α 3区域有敌机侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙  Damocles的钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,δ区域  通信中断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六浮空装置控制室被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈泽尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要我使出最后的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这Damocles将成为捕捉鲁路修他们的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们脱离之后  用F.L.E.I.J.A.将Damocles整个消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是宏伟的灵柩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修应该会喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Damocles上升到了卫星轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算Lancelot也无计可施的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赢就得压制修奈泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在分析内部构造
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析密码锁…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季诺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不承认你的布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  这力量是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季诺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修  你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有必须打倒的敌人和必须救助的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季诺  如论如何都要跟我一战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  为了我心中要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要守护的东西  我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护？  你要守护什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈泽尔在管制指令层吗  还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F.L.E.I.J.A.起爆位置变更为Damocles本体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damocles和F.L.E.I.J.A.  终究不过是机械
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再造过就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  Tromo机关已经没有这种余力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗森堡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在全世界都是鲁路修的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为消灭了鲁路修的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种组织都会乐意给我们制造F.L.E.I.J.A.的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不会导致与恐怖主义发生联系的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是应该问问娜娜莉殿下的意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个必要  区区诱饵的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要抛弃她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界和平与区区一条人命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可悲  但这是不能相比的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙  钥匙在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要阻止哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是桥头堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阁下的作战成功之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌现在的鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六骑士？!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得作为我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为国家  也不为复仇  更没有野心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有战斗理由之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要参和进来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由已经有了  那就是约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说你喜欢鲁路修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是想结束经验的积累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会说人话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华莲  你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然还会有输赢的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙  钥匙在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要阻止哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哈尔特格伦卿的汇合地点  没有变更
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了  修奈泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  被将军的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我  为什么会知道我的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是策略  我看穿的是你的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本质？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没打算要获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱禁城的对局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团的政变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是在绝不会输的地方进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你认为我会放弃Damocles？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈泽尔  这次我一定要让你输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  要杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洪古从第三通道压制舰桥  各国代表的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天子陛下  您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻大人  我们是站在你们那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说你们背叛了鲁路修？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是被威胁的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  既然鲁路修已经不在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在否定独裁者的意义上  应该可以信任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  决战似乎缩小到Damocles内部了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇先生…事务总长也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  他们都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后  皇兄还是没有杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇兄没有执着的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生若逢时  他理应能成为卓越之王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能看穿这点  我太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还愿意那样称呼我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想用Damocles控制世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我只是想创造人们都期望的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无视人的本质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见解不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想将世界固定在「今天」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  没有变化的日常不能称之为生存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那仅仅是经验罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  它的连续就是知识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为太过优秀才看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  皇帝查理追求的是昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你追求的是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我想要的是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也许比今天更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  会变得更好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无论花多少时间  人都会不断地追求幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那分明将会为欲望所绊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不过是感情罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为希望和梦想的不可靠的虚构
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是在皇族的记号下俯视世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与不幸抗争之人  追求未来之人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在期盼着幸福  不断的抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass也好  假面也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其根源就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自相矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直否认他人意志的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时却要肯定人的意志  肯定人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你也会被F.L.E.I.J.A.消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我们的生命来换取世界的和平…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要赠你一句话——「遵从Zero吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从一开始就不是想要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿…殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我没察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是看穿了修奈泽尔思考方式的录像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨听主命  Zero大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈泽尔  你认为自己会被杀的想法导致了你的败北
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  你的故事已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无权否认我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈泽尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便对自己的性命无所依恋的人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Geass的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  至少在最后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我使用Geass…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪特哈尔特  对你没有施加Geass的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  修奈泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先给我解除Damocles的自爆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  F.L.E.I.J.A.的控制开关在娜娜莉手上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何强化机体  你都赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真敢说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是结果  季诺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我的任务已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把BLAZELUMINOUS的系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  华莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  季诺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  是时候做个了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们各自相违的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥  吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的目的是这Damocles的钥匙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这东西对你而言太过危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再逃避视线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破了他的Geass？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自己的意志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  也要对我使用Geass吗


